    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term applied to lavishly ornamented standing salts, such as those used on the high table at ceremonial banquets.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000021291/Newman, Illustrated Dictionary of Silverware (1987)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Término que se aplica a saleros de caldero espléndidamente ornamentados, como aquellos que se usan en la mesa principal de banquetes ceremoniales. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rijkbewerkte zoutvaten op voet, zoals gebruikt op de hoge tafel bij ceremoniële banketten. Geen Nederlands equivalent. Zie 'zoutvaten'.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指裝飾華麗的立式鹽瓶，例如置於儀式或宴會中貴賓桌上者。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
